{
  "stem": "12052.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when there came orders and put us in the lower camp, there was terrible-- there were people sick with typhoid, with dysentery, with diarrhea, with-- people couldn't control and just bleed to death through their through their stomach and-- so that was a terrible nightmare.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a while, I-- I met some Russian prisoners only they were from, like, Uzbekistan and-- and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow I could organize and get a little bit extra soup, what was warm water, what-- with nothing in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- How did you manage to get the extra?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian prisoners, I met them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I befriended some of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And and that was terrible, while we didn't get any bread and any food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was end of the-- end of-- ending of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I later on was transferred to a barracks where there were kids, kids, young people from we say, from 10 or nine till about 16.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was more than.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One second-- '45 is-- yeah, about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there we got a little bit better treatment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have to stay all night in frost outside and counting and-- for punishment people were flying-- falling like flies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every morning you got up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you could sleep a little bit, you got up and you saw outside big [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] piles of dead people, sometime 50, sometime 100, sometime even more people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What they throw there on the pile, they were just skin and bone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were taken on wagon drawn by the prisoners to crematorium and burned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or some of them just didn't have time to burn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just were in ditches there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was a very, very bad and depressing time over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
